    <img
      src="/betalan/tournaments/StepMania.png"
      alt="StepMania Competition"
      class="responsive-img"
    />
    <h2 class="section-title">What is the StepMania Competition?</h2>

    <p class="paragraph">
      StepMania is a rhythm game where you step
       on the arrows with your feet to follow the arrows on the screen, making you dance along the song!
       We'll be playing through a series of random songs, where the highest score
        bewteen the two players against each other, moves on through the Bracket till we have a winner!
        So join the competition and show off your dance moves!
    </p>

